WEBVTT

00:01.301 --> 00:03.502
<i>Thanks for
downloading this fox show.</i>

00:03.504 --> 00:05.738
<i>And don't miss
all-new episodes on fox.</i>

00:06.939 --> 00:08.807
<i>Previously on sleepy hollow...</i>

00:08.809 --> 00:12.644
Hey, demon! To hell,
from whence you came.

00:12.646 --> 00:13.779
No!

00:15.016 --> 00:15.981
Dreyfuss, it's over!

00:15.983 --> 00:16.949
<i>I ask this great stone</i>

00:16.951 --> 00:19.351
<i>to transform to the elixir</i>

00:19.353 --> 00:21.120
<i>of everliving life.</i>

00:23.957 --> 00:26.525
A witness is no different
from any other person.

00:26.527 --> 00:27.659
Except that
they're a monster magnet.

00:27.661 --> 00:29.661
You can try
and deny what's happening,

00:29.663 --> 00:31.330
<i>and sooner or later,
it's gonna catch up to you.</i>

00:31.332 --> 00:32.631
<i>And Molly, too.</i>

00:32.633 --> 00:33.966
<i>The only thing I have to do</i>

00:33.968 --> 00:36.201
<i>is protect my daughter.</i>

